style.css
.image{

border-color:#999900;

border-width:2px;

border-style:solid;

border-radius:15px;

border-bottom-style:dotted;

border-bottom-width:10px;

border-bottom-color:red;

}



Notes:
border-radius: 10px;

The way for you to specify which corner you wanne curve.
border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
border-top-left-radius: 10px;
border-top-right-radius: 10px;

border-bottom-style|width|color: dotted|2px|red;
border-top
border-right
border-left

Can apply these against style, width, color.
